y" about="#mwt296" id="mwCOw"> </span><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A2002.02.0006%3Asura%3D101%3Averse%3D1" about="#mwt296" id="mwCO0">101:1</a></span></li><li about="#cite_note-Mahdi1-97" id="cite_note-Mahdi1-97"><a href="./Islam#cite_ref-Mahdi1_97-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-Mahdi1-97" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation book" about="#mwt299" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"last":{"wt":"Yahya"},"first":{"wt":"Harun"},"authorlink":{"wt":""},"author2":{"wt":""},"title":{"wt":"Portents And Features of the Mahdi&apos;s Coming"},"publisher":{"wt":"Global Publishing. Kindle Edition"},"date":{"wt":"12 May 2010"},"location":{"wt":""},"pages":{"wt":""},"url":{"wt":""},"doi":{"wt":""},"id":{"wt":""}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwCO4">Yahya, Harun (12 May 2010). <i id="mwCO8">Portents And Features of the Mahdi's Coming</i>. Global Publishing. Kindle Edition.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Portents+And+Features+of+the+Mahdi%27s+Coming&amp;rft.pub=Global+Publishing.+Kindle+Edition&amp;rft.date=2010-05-12&amp;rft.aulast=Yahya&amp;rft.aufirst=Harun&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AIslam" class="Z3988" about="#mwt299" id="mwCPA"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt299" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwCPE"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-98" id="cite_note-98"><a href="./Islam#cite_ref-98" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-98" class="mw-reference-text"><ul id="mwCPI"><li id="mwCPM"